  <brief_title>Study of VIR-2218 in Healthy Volunteers and Patients With Chronic Hepatitis B</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1/2, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics, and Antiviral Activity of VIR-2218</official_title>
  <sponsors>
