  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a phase 1/2 study in which healthy volunteers and subjects with chronic HBV infection
      will receive VIR-2218 or placebo and will be assessed for safety, tolerability,
      pharmacokinetics, and antiviral activity (only in subjects with chronic HBV).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
